evidence.text: The case was dismissed without prejudice on March 10, 2025 (Docket Entry 207) without any mention of monitoring or a monitoring order. All documents (Complaint, Motion for Preliminary Injunction, Docket entries) contain no reference to a court-appointed monitor or monitoring reports.

ORDER OF DISMISSAL: Considering the foregoing Stipulation of Dismissal (Rec. Doc. 206 ), IT IS HEREBY ORDERED that the above-numbered and entitled cause is DISMISSED without the admission of any issue of fact or law, with each party to bear its own costs. Signed by Judge Carl J Barbier on 3/10/2025.
